panels.content:
Select a Country from the list above.

This dashboard shows the flow data for the selected country.
The sankey graph shows the top 10 senders and receivers by volume. Thicker lines indicate greater flows.
The tables show top 10 by both volume and rate as well as top talker organizations. Other flow stats are also included at the bottom.
